Real Racing 3: Keroxea Edition

The aim of this version is to allow for extended play without altering the game's original structure.
The original game has been preserved in anticipation of the expected server outage on May 20th.

This version was developed to preserve the original state of the game.
The game's size has been efficiently reduced (1.4 GB)
Graphical adjustments have been made to improve game performance.
Time Shifted Multiplayer was initially designed to work offline.
Daily tasks refresh without a network connection in version 1.0.56.
Incompatibility issues between the main package and asset packages have been resolved.
Xiaomi HyperOS system-specific compatibility has been added. The game will not be affected by server issues even if the internet is on.
Since there is no M$ in the versions, the game can be played completely without an internet connection.
Compatibility issues have been resolved. The game runs on devices with Adreno GPUs.
Game archiving system was controlled by a Samsung Galaxy Wonder (GT-I8150).
The archive was first tested on Android 4.4.4 KitKat with Cyanogenmod 11 operating system.
This archive was compiled by Qualcomm Snapdragon S2 MSM8255.
GPU Ä°nfo: 1x1.4 GHz Scorpion (Adreno 205)


